name: "Haystack - Balloon - Bridge" by Eva LoveBux
description:
This is an 1/1 original painting by Eva LoveBux

Eva is the daughter of NFT Artist HP LoveBuX.

This TEZ wallet has been set up for her by her father and all funds
are sent there are for her to draw upon in the future.

She is a meticulous artist and always produces wonderful work.

Your investment in her talent today may be a great boon
to her when the time comes for her to pursue a college
education. 

So, please buy and re-sell the art if you like it.

Best Regards,

The LoveBux Family
Ira, Eva, and HP
